    <item>
      <title>Topgolf Callaway 在否认交易报道后削减涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/topgolf-callaway-soars-on-report-it-s-exploring-sale-spinoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级高尔夫卡拉威品牌公司 (Topgolf Callaway Brands Corp.) 驳斥了早些时候的一份报道，该报道称该公司正在考虑出售其高尔夫装备部门，并表示不知道有任何出售该业务的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/topgolf-callaway-soars-on-report-it-s-exploring-sale-spinoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国中化集团从加拿大管道购买第一批石油货物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/china-s-sinochem-takes-first-oil-cargo-from-canadian-pipeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国中化集团购买了首批原油货物之一，这些原油将通过一条新的加拿大管道运输，该管道旨在将更多石油从内陆阿尔伯塔省输送到太平洋海岸进行出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/china-s-sinochem-takes-first-oil-cargo-from-canadian-pipeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 02:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
